name: "What Lies Before Us" - photo by HPLOVEBUX
description:
We look ahead, wondering.
We are still the children we were.
We aim to occupy the story we write.
The future never ages, and the next
generation takes over when our footsteps 
cease. 

This photo is offered for DPZ's event on 12/3/21
If you enjoy this please seek out my other work.

Thanks and all best wishes,

HP LoveBux
